{"tid":1220260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好玩宗教，唔好玩宗教，唔好玩宗教！！！","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T03:59:09.000Z","uid":133611,"like":78,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"85c4f92eaccfad145a6b9aa267317d60c6425d24","tid":1220260,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"你想用宗教嘅力量，你本身唔信教唔係問題<br />\n但係你要諗下你係咪清楚人地宗教先？<br />\n你知道人地會點做？<br />\n一間你鬧出笑話<br />\n或人地一睇就知你玩嘢、假冒<br />\n咁就好大獲，佢地唔會再幫你！！！<br />\neg. 真正基督徒/佛教徒係唔會拎住本聖經去勇武<br />\n<br />\n見到有人話有冇佛教徒/其他宗教<br />\n就唔該你哋就真係做返嗰個教嘅人會做嘅嘢<br />\n或者直接啲去感化嗰個教嘅人 一齊去支持<br />\n<br />\n不要假冒其他宗教人仕<br />\n不要拎有宗教代表性嘅嘢做武器！！"},{"pid":"c2cae5268d2d15a7a1f238ea6d2da527aa31b3fc","tid":1220260,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5387179b6d4fa5007ad1ca76236a0df43ccd2f7","tid":1220260,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"96f01c90d8a4d4f19c7198b9a55cb03286c9e431","tid":1220260,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5387179b6d4fa5007ad1ca76236a0df43ccd2f7","tid":1220260,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:33:07.000Z","msg":"法國黃背心運動的 8 堂課<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1219915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1219915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"呢個值得學習"},{"pid":"903ab8c5921744e72ff481862066943345dfb5c6","tid":1220260,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8023ba5ba17a98cdae980481c12169032cbc455","tid":1220260,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T04:02:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8f0869fc58a2cfe8